data.description: Recently updated 2bd 2ba home in Brooktrails. All fresh paint inside and out, new laminate flooring throughout home. New roof installed June 2023. Furnace replaced in the last couple of years. Garage is wired for a backup generator. Large deck surrounding front and side of home. Large lot with a 2nd lot with it's own water rights make it perfect to add a second home or and ADU. Located on a quiet dead end street making it feel private yet only minutes to town and Hwy 101 for an easy commute to surrounding areas. This home needs nothing and is move in ready. This is a must see!!
